==Korean==
===Verb===
'''만들다''' (''mandeul-da'')
#To [[make]]
#:종이 비행기를 '''만들다'''. (''jongI bihaengi-reul '''mandeulda''''') To make a paper airplane. 
#: 친구를 '''만들다'''. (''Chingu-reul mandeulda'') To make friends. 
#To [[establish]] (a law, club, etc.)
#:시대에 맞는 헌법을 '''만들다'''. (''Sidae-e maj-neun heonbeob-eul '''mandeulda''''') To establish a constitution suited to the times.

